modules.description: This module creates a graphical interface for interacting with Mlpost figures using GTK. It supports adding text inputs that trigger updates to the displayed figure, radio menus for selecting options, and dynamically displaying or removing figure windows. Use it to build simple interactive visualizations where user input controls the generation and appearance of Mlpost graphics.

This module integrates Mlpost figures with GTK to create interactive graphical interfaces. It provides functions to define aspect ratio behaviors for figure scaling and supports building UIs with input controls that dynamically update displayed graphics. Use it to create responsive visualizations where user input adjusts Mlpost-generated images in real time.
